WEBVTT

00:00.661 --> 00:03.018
<i>Previously on
AMC's Mad Men...</i>

00:03.194 --> 00:04.635
I think it'd be helpful

00:04.786 --> 00:06.603
if you and I were
to meet once a month

00:06.721 --> 00:08.880
just to, you know,
keep up with Sally's progress.

00:09.607 --> 00:12.238
I hate it here.
I really really do.

00:13.023 --> 00:14.023
I won't tell anybody.

00:14.264 --> 00:16.383
I don't have to live
with your shit over my head.

00:17.841 --> 00:20.256
- What's going on?
- We lost Lucky Strike.

00:21.176 --> 00:25.024
I got you a meeting with Heinz. They're
at Ketchum McLeod and they're restless.

00:25.238 --> 00:26.144
You didn't have to do this.

00:28.569 --> 00:29.730
I wanted to.

